quran[22]{c,v,t}:
  85,1,Mi woondirii kammu jom …óate ngun
  85,2,O woondirii √±alawma podaa…óo o
  85,3,O woodarii kala ceedii…óo e kala ko seedaa…óo
  85,4,Hu…óaama yim…ìe Ukhduud-fettin…ìe leydi petti maw…ói
  85,5,Yiite marnge ku…ì…ìam
  85,6,Tuma nde …ìe joo…ói e dow mannge
  85,7,Kam…ìe ko…ìe mba…óata ko goon…óin…ìe …ìe ko…ìe seedii…ìe
  85,8,…ìe njoftiraaki …ìe si wonah …ìe ngoon…óinii Alla teddu…óo jettaa…óo
  85,9,Ko Alla Woodani Laamu kammuuli …óin e leydi ndin. Alla ko Kattan…óo kala huunde
  85,10,…ìeen faw…ìe e dow juul…ìe rew…ìe e wor…ìe fitina refti …ìe tuubaani woodanii…ìe lepte jahannama woodanii…ìe lepte cumooje
  85,11,…ìeen goon…óin…ìe ngoolli golle lobbe woodanii…ìe Aljannaaji na ila ley mum caatli ko …óuum woni malal manngal. @Corrected
  85,12,Pellet nanngannde joom ma ko sattunde
  85,13,Ko Kanko tigi fu…ó…óata tagu O rutta mbo
  85,14,Ko Kanko woni Yaafatoo…óo Gi…óo
  85,15,Mbo arsi teddu…óo woodani. @Corrected
  85,16,Ba…óoowo ko O welaa
  85,17,taw si arii e maa…óa Yewtere fii Muusaa
  85,18,Fir*awna e Samuud
  85,19,Accu yeddu…ìe …ìe ngoni ko e fennude
  85,20,Alla na fiiltarii…ìe caggal
  85,21,Kammbo ko mbo Quraana teddu…óo
  85,22,Hombo e alluwal deenangal
